::Hot Rod::

"Ok, help CliffJumper."
Hot Rod syands ready to defend his old Autobot friend.

::Epyon:;

He looks at Depth Charge.
"Be my guest."
He soars away as Rampage charges in.

::DrillBit::

He runs out with Killfests troops, and starts drilling through the
ground towards the CF. He gives orders for the Pack to follow over the
comm link.

::Dollon::

He follows DrillBit.

::Demolition::

He also looks at Wolfgang questioning this bot. He thinks he commands
the Alliance, and the War Machines were intruders?

::KitKat2::

She starts looking through the records on the computers. She learns
where she was, and all about the KitKat3 clone. She needed to get out.
